  <div class="page-container">
  <h3>How to take a screenshot with keyboard shortcuts</h3>
  <h5>03 Feb 2026</h5>
  
  <p>Check out Wikipedia's list of keyboard shortcuts <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Table_of_keyboard_shortcuts#General_shortcuts">here</a>!</p>
  
  <p><strong>If you have a Mac...</strong></p>
  
  <div class="list-bg">
  <ul>
    <li>For a full screen, press <kbd>Command</kbd> + <kbd>Shift</kbd> + <kbd>3</kbd></li>
    <li>For a selected area, press <kbd>Command</kbd> + <kbd>Shift</kbd> + <kbd>4</kbd></li>
  </ul>
  </div>
  
  <p><strong>If you have a Windows...</strong></p>
  
  <div class="list-bg">
  <ul>
    <li>For a full screen, press <kbd>Windows</kbd> + <kbd>PrtScn</kbd></li>
    <li>For a selected area, press <kbd>Windows</kbd> + <kbd>Shift</kbd> + <kbd>S</kbd></li>
  </ul>
  </div>
  </div>
  
